1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
English subtitles are available

2
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:48,520
Just in Time EP19

3
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,800
Help?

4
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,680
Please help.

5
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,680
Let's go!

6
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,120
Right now.

7
00:01:59,919 --> 00:02:00,760
Listen to me.

8
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,920
Who's gone?

9
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,559
Meng'an.

10
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,719
She's in a hurry.

11
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:29,360
Before going to work,

12
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,520
she'll pay a visit to her father.

13
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,200
No way!

14
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:31,960
She hasn't taken the medicine!

15
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,439
She won't!

16
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,719
I... I'll take it.

17
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,200
Nonsense!

18
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,480
You take it for what?

19
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,999
Let me tell you.

20
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:40,520
Inform me as soon as she's back.

21
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:41,759
I'll boil the medicine for her.

22
00:02:41,999 --> 00:02:43,360
Two times a day.

23
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,999
Adhere strictly to my prescription.

24
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,159
Do you hear me?

25
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,719
See?

26
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,559
The dosage is for half a month.

27
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:58,319
Why didn't you knock the door?

28
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,480
For what?

29
00:02:59,559 --> 00:03:00,960
You're not bare to the waist.

30
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,159
I'm your sister.

31
00:03:03,279 --> 00:03:04,080
What do you want?

32
00:03:04,279 --> 00:03:05,319
Where are you going?

33
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,279
Going for work!

34
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,719
Get dressed,

35
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:08,999
and talk with me.

36
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:15,879
Five minutes.

37
00:03:15,999 --> 00:03:16,559
Hurry up.

38
00:03:16,999 --> 00:03:17,400
Sit down.

39
00:03:17,999 --> 00:03:19,120
Just spit it out.

40
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,400
Sit down!

41
00:03:21,559 --> 00:03:22,200
Sis,

42
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:24,360
I'm in my forties.

43
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,080
Don't treat me like a kid!

44
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,800
But you'll always be my brother.

45
00:03:29,279 --> 00:03:29,920
Just say it.

46
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:30,879
You say first.

47
00:03:31,279 --> 00:03:32,319
Say what?

48
00:03:32,559 --> 00:03:33,400
Our family maxim.

49
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,960
Parental and fraternal bonds

50
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,960
unite family members all.

51
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,159
Exactly!

52
00:03:41,559 --> 00:03:43,439
A peaceful family will be prosperous,

53
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,159
right?

54
00:03:44,559 --> 00:03:45,920
Our mother died young,

55
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:49,120
and father had to run the clinic alone.

56
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:51,200
All household chores

57
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,960
had been my responsibility.

58
00:03:53,999 --> 00:03:55,279
Before our father passed away,

59
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:58,080
he asked Ouyang to marry into our family.

60
00:03:58,839 --> 00:03:59,599
He ordered me

61
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,920
to discipline you,

62
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,120
so that you would be a talent.

63
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,640
You didn't disappoint us.

64
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,999
I never worried about your study.

65
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,279
Afterwards,

66
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:09,520
you married Meng'an, a good wife.

67
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,240
See?

68
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,360
What a happy life!

69
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:13,719
For these years,

70
00:04:13,999 --> 00:04:15,879
I've never disturbed your life.

71
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,599
Well,

72
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,920
what's your key point?

73
00:04:22,159 --> 00:04:23,960
It's the key period now.

74
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,480
The key period of what?

75
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,680
It's the key period of our Li family

76
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:30,079
to raise offspring now.

77
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,040
Get it?

78
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,319
There are not many

79
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:34,240
key periods in one's life.

80
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,800
We can only count them

81
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,360
with four fingers.

82
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:37,920
Birth,

83
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,360
age,

84
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:38,920
illness,

85
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,439
and death.

86
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,800
Birth ranks the first.

87
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,399
Li Lin,

88
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:45,199
you should pick up your spirits!

89
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,879
Why? Do I look discouraged?

90
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:48,079
Why must I pick up my spirits?

91
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,959
I'm not pregnant!

92
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:50,879
Don't beat around the bush!

93
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,360
Though Meng'an is pregnant,

94
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,879
you don't want to keep the baby,

95
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:54,360
do you?

96
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,319
Of course we'll keep the baby!

97
00:04:56,999 --> 00:04:57,959
From whom did you hear the rumor?

98
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,600
It's none of your business.

99
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,759
I'll forget about the truth

100
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:03,600
that you didn't tell me.

101
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,680
I understand that you want to

102
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,999
hide it away from me.

103
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:07,600
In our opinion,

104
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,600
let nature take its course.

105
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:11,480
The baby appears unexpectedly.

106
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,360
If God keeps it,

107
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,959
we'll keep it;

108
00:05:14,999 --> 00:05:16,120
if it's not strong enough,

109
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,399
we have no other choice.

110
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,879
How come?

111
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,600
Our Li Family has studied

112
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,480
TCM for generations.

113
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,280
No doubt we have choices!

114
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,160
It is true that

115
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,199
we've studied TCM for long,

116
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,319
but you're not a doctor.

117
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:29,319
Do you have ways to keep the baby?

118
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,759
I am the way.

119
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:33,280
I've arranged everything properly.

120
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,600
I arranged Lanxiang

121
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,920
to look after your father-in-law.

122
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,120
As for me,

123
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,160
I'll stay here

124
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,720
to look after you.

125
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,280
You?

126
00:05:45,959 --> 00:05:46,439
Yes.

127
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,920
Stay here?

128
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,920
Yes.

129
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,319
I have my duty to stay here,

130
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,079
which is to help the Li Family

131
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:54,680
to

132
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,360
raise

133
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:55,920
the

134
00:05:55,959 --> 00:05:56,680
offspring!

135
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,319
What takes you so long?

136
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,680
I'm going late for work.

137
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:05,800
You ran away,

138
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:07,079
but I failed.

139
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,519
She was disciplining me back there.

140
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,480
I knew it.

141
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,480
She's prepared

142
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,680
to stay in our house.

143
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,800
Lanxiang is unreliable!

144
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,840
Forget it.

145
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,399
Anyway,

146
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,759
we can face the challenge.

147
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,519
Don't worry.

148
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,480
I'll let her go back.

149
00:06:31,999 --> 00:06:32,800
Is it appropriate?

150
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,280
I think so.

151
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,959
When you gave birth to Yunjie,

152
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,480
she was in our house, remember?

153
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,720
Like a backseat driver.

154
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,120
Weren't you angry?

155
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,120
I was.

156
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,120
See?

157
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:45,559
But we were young back then.

158
00:06:45,559 --> 00:06:46,840
In the twenties,

159
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,600
we had big egos.

160
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,480
Things are different now.

161
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:52,600
If someone can give me a hand now,

162
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,120
I'll be glad.

163
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,040
Besides, back then,

164
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,360
some of her words made sense.

165
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,999
She's the head nurse, anyway.

166
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,240
How ridiculous!

167
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,160
Working in her own clinic,

168
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,319
she can be the head of clinic!

169
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,360
Well,

170
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,519
I'm afraid she'll cause trouble

171
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,319
to you.

172
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,399
I admit she's a good person,

173
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,920
but disregards social distance.

174
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,319
While I was getting myself dressed,

175
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,199
she came in

176
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:16,319
without knocking on the door,

177
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,199
giving me a start.

178
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:19,639
So embarrassing!

179
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,160
If you were not pregnant,

180
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,240
she could live here

181
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,559
as long as she wished.

182
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:24,519
It doesn't matter,

183
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,999
though sometimes she might be bossy.

184
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,120
Things are different now

185
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,559
since a baby comes.

186
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,120
If in case that

187
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,879
something wrong happens to you,

188
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,240
let alone going to work,

189
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,079
she won't even allow you to go out!

190
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,800
Don't you trust me?

191
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,319
I do, I do.

192
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,680
In that case,

193
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,680
you try to ask her.

194
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,160
Fine.

195
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,120
I'll have a try.

196
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:50,920
Don't worry.

197
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,399
I won't infuriate her.

198
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,800
If she doesn't want to leave,

199
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,559
don't be too tough.

200
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:55,559
I won't.

201
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,480
Unlike her,

202
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,399
I know the limit.

203
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,680
The job can't be lost!

204
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,639
How dare you bring a phone here?

205
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:23,680
I'll take it!

206
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,519
My heart missed a beat!

207
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,639
Last night,

208
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,199
were it not me saving the situation,

209
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,240
my mother might give up

210
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,120
the baby!

211
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,439
Don't you believe me?

212
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,920
Do you know how I told my mother?

213
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,800
Last night,

214
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:39,439
my parents didn't

215
00:08:39,439 --> 00:08:40,440
come back until midnight.

216
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,960
I was waiting in the living room.

217
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,159
Even so, my mother scolded me,

218
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,480
"Good for you, Li Yunjie!

219
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,759
How dare you stay up late?"

220
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,399
Do you know what I said?

221
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,200
What did you say?

222
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,360
"Woman,

223
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:52,799
I have a word with you.

224
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,679
The baby in your womb

225
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,679
must be kept.

226
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,759
Dad dares not tell you,

227
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,799
but I do.

228
00:08:58,999 --> 00:09:00,759
I won't make any recession,

229
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:02,159
and it all depends on your attitude."

230
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,159
What did your mom say?

231
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,480
My mom said,

232
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:05,879
"Good for you, Li Yunjie!

233
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:06,999
How dare you

234
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,120
speak to me like that?"

235
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,279
But she promised me eventually.

236
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,320
In our home,

237
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,440
my dad's not a decision-maker,

238
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,960
and he discusses everything with her.

239
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:16,120
How tiring!

240
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,720
You're so naive!

241
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,519
Afterwards,

242
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:19,519
your life will be miserable.

243
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,879
Stop being so serious!

244
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,679
The baby is my little sister.

245
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,679
Just leave it to me.

246
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:26,080
How do you know it's a she?

247
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,399
What if it's a he?

248
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,399
You are doomed to be miserable!

249
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:32,080
It'll be fine.

250
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,600
My dad will be my supporter.

251
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:34,639
Anyway,

252
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:35,960
everything at home

253
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,399
is under my control.

254
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:40,639
Stop bragging!

255
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:42,720
Under your control?

256
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:46,919
Woman, I have a word with you!

257
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,080
I'm so afraid!

258
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,679
I'm so afraid!

259
00:09:51,919 --> 00:09:52,879
Stop it!

260
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,120
Little Watermelon, cheer up!

261
00:09:55,999 --> 00:09:56,759
Cheer up!

262
00:09:56,999 --> 00:09:57,639
Little Watermelon,

263
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,560
mom's visiting you.

264
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:01,039
Your mom is a beauty.

265
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,679
Once you can see her,

266
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:05,080
you'll be a beauty yourself!

267
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,720
Cheer up, Little Watermelon!

268
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:09,480
Little Watermelon?

269
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:11,080
Who gave her such a name?

270
00:10:11,279 --> 00:10:11,919
Darling,

271
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,879
the name is given by Xiongxiong.

272
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,360
Given such a name,

273
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,360
She'll be easily raised.

274
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,679
Our baby is a girl,

275
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,919
so it sounds terrible

276
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:19,879
to be called Little Watermelon!

277
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,600
Sweet.

278
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:22,759
Sweet girl.

279
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:24,720
Darling,

280
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:26,200
does your wound hurt?

281
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:26,679
Darling,

282
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:27,960
I'm so sorry.

283
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,080
So sorry about that.

284
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,039
It's all my fault.

285
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:30,879
Darling.

286
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,960
If you didn't sign your name,

287
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:35,039
my belly wouldn't have suffered!

288
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:36,999
Darling,

289
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,799
I had no gut to sign my name.

290
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,679
Let me tell you,

291
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,279
it was your sister.

292
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:45,080
You didn't sign your name?

293
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:48,320
I... I just offered up

294
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:49,639
a hand.

295
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:53,919
Darling.

296
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:54,600
Darling.

297
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,279
I'm so sorry.

