1188
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:19,880
Yes.

1189
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:21,199
Who are you?

1190
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,120
You must be her matron!

1191
00:41:24,639 --> 00:41:26,400
These are fruits for Mengxin.

1192
00:41:26,759 --> 00:41:28,000
Wash them later

1193
00:41:28,359 --> 00:41:29,359
for Mengxin.

1194
00:41:29,759 --> 00:41:30,719
Wait.

1195
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:32,400
Who on earth are you?

1196
00:41:33,560 --> 00:41:35,000
