1197
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:36,199
How couldn't I?

1198
00:41:36,239 --> 00:41:37,480
Are you speaking a foreign language?

1199
00:41:40,679 --> 00:41:42,159
I do apologize.

1200
00:41:42,520 --> 00:41:43,159
Well,

1201
00:41:43,719 --> 00:41:44,719
you must

1202
00:41:45,639 --> 00:41:47,159
be the baby's grandma, aren't you?

1203
00:41:49,359 --> 00:41:50,719
Sorry for my stupidity!

1204
00:41:50,839 --> 00:41:51,960
I do apologize.

1205
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:53,639
I hope you can forgive me.

1206
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,319
Darling,

1207
00:41:54,679 --> 00:41:55,839
it's still warm. Have a taste.

1208
00:41:58,319 --> 00:41:59,480
I'll take a snap.

1209
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:02,319
Okay.

1210
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,839
If you want to sleep,

1211
00:42:04,159 --> 00:42:04,799
I'll be there for you.

1212
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:06,799
Eat it after you're awake.

1213
00:42:07,719 --> 00:42:08,639
So tell me.

1214
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:10,000
Who on earth are you?

1215
00:42:10,719 --> 00:42:11,799
I am Li Jing,

1216
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,359
the sister of Li Lin,

1217
00:42:13,359 --> 00:42:15,159
who is the husband of Meng'an,

1218
00:42:15,159 --> 00:42:17,120
the sister of Mengxin.

1219
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,560
Fine, I get it.

1220
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:20,759
Sister-in-law of the Xu Family.

1221
00:42:21,159 --> 00:42:21,719
There you go,

1222
00:42:22,199 --> 00:42:23,000
