1226
00:42:27,319 --> 00:42:28,679
I'm not your dear sister!

1227
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:31,359
I'm Xiongxiong's grandmother,

1228
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:32,560
while you are his

1229
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:34,759
distant aunt!

1230
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:36,199
You should call me...

1231
00:42:36,239 --> 00:42:37,199
Auntie!

1232
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,480
Right.

1233
00:42:38,839 --> 00:42:40,400
You're my auntie.

1234
00:42:41,600 --> 00:42:43,159
The yummy sweets

1235
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:45,000
are still warm.

1236
00:43:02,799 --> 00:43:04,159
Let me explain it to you.

1237
00:43:04,400 --> 00:43:05,239
Meng'an

1238
00:43:05,239 --> 00:43:06,520
is pregnant,

1239
00:43:06,679 --> 00:43:08,120
so I'll take care of her.

1240
00:43:08,120 --> 00:43:10,199
