1243
00:43:13,359 --> 00:43:14,440
A piece of luck.

1244
00:43:14,520 --> 00:43:14,960
You see,

1245
00:43:15,199 --> 00:43:16,000
it's a present

1246
00:43:16,560 --> 00:43:18,159
for our dear baby.

1247
00:43:18,400 --> 00:43:20,839
How blessed you are!

1248
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:22,560
