1250
00:43:27,120 --> 00:43:28,639
Fine. Follow me.

1251
00:43:28,639 --> 00:43:30,080
I'll put it aside.

1252
00:43:35,080 --> 00:43:36,040
Auntie,

1253
00:43:36,359 --> 00:43:37,239
I'll take it.

1254
00:43:37,480 --> 00:43:37,920
Go away!

1255
00:43:37,920 --> 00:43:38,560
Okay.

1256
00:43:38,560 --> 00:43:39,600
Follow me.

